程序包 org.janusgraph.graphdb.query.graph

类 GraphCentricQueryBuilder

java.lang.Object
org.janusgraph.graphdb.query.graph.GraphCentricQueryBuilder
所有已实现的接口:
JanusGraphQuery<GraphCentricQueryBuilder>
public class GraphCentricQueryBuilder
extends Object
implements JanusGraphQuery<GraphCentricQueryBuilder>
Builds a JanusGraphQuery, optimizes the query and compiles the result into a GraphCentricQuery which is then executed through a QueryProcessor.
作者:
Matthias Broecheler (me@matthiasb.com)
